text:
The food was very enjoyable
The pig stomach soup taste was well balanced. And the serving was generous

The skewers for bbq was very reasonably priced and it was very good as well
The charcoal experience was fun

All was well
Service was prompt and friendly

The atmosphere at this coffee shop was great and vibrant

I had a good time and will visit again
Food was good, price was reasonable and staffs were extremely friendly. Highly recommended!

The pig stomach soup is really yummy. Generous portion of pig stomach and other ingredients. Highly recommended. The portion looks more  suitable for 3. The price is reasonable.

Most of the lok-lok sticks are between $1 to $3. Meal comes with free plate of fruits. The staff is also very nice. Refill of soup is free.

We were so full after the meal.
